All G buttons are universal. If it's not your mouse doesn't matter. Middle mouse button is always 3.
For Example Left side buttons are always 4 and 5. It's always the same. 

When the script is activated the capslock light will goes ON from your keyboard.
With clicking again the same button the weapon will be deactivated also the light from keyboard turns off. (If you have a light on keyboard)

